&lt;li&gt;Active Times        :Hello 2s MaxAge 20s FwDly 15s MaxHop 20&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;CIST Root/ERPC      :0    .4c1f-ccc2-5dc2 / 200000&lt;/li&gt;
