Reply from 10.0.23.3: bytes=56 Sequence=3 ttl=255 time=30 ms&lt;br&gt;
Reply from 10.0.23.3: bytes=56 Sequence=4 ttl=255 time=20 ms&lt;br&gt;
Reply from 10.0.23.3: bytes=56 Sequence=5 ttl=255 time=20 ms&lt;/li&gt;
